
1. build the library
	make
   libnvm.a is generated.

2. cleanup the directory
	make clean

3. change the configure file: nvm_config

4. include src/nvm.h in your .c files

5. call nvm_init() at the beginning of your main() function

6. call nvm_exit() at the end of your main() function

7. compile your program
	gcc example.c -L. -lnvm -o example

